{"type":"message","id":"aab9b7be","parentId":"82cdeb54","timestamp":"2026-04-18T01:18:27.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To set up your Telegram integration, we'll need to follow a few steps. Since this involves connecting an external account, I'll need to guide you through the necessary process.\n\nGenerally, this involves:\n\n1.  **Getting a Bot Token:** If you are setting up a bot, you'll need to talk to BotFather on Telegram to create one and get an API token.\n2.  **OAuth or Linking:** Then, we'll use the appropriate OpenClaw tool/skill to link your account or bot to the system.\n\nCould you clarify if you are trying to:\n\n*   **A) Set up a personal account** (i.e., you want me to read or interact with your personal Telegram messages)?\n*   **B) Set up a dedicated Bot** (i.e., you want me to manage messages from a bot you created)?\n\nOnce I know that, I can check my available skills to see the best procedure."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:e4b","usage":{"input":14865,"output":202,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15067,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776475107428}}
