{"type":"message","id":"f6ec8fba","parentId":"fe1ec6cd","timestamp":"2026-04-22T13:56:34.456Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-22 06:30:36 PDT] GOOD MORNING\nSystem: \nSystem: BIBLE\nSystem: Proverbs 27:17 — \"As iron sharpens iron, so one person sharpens another.\" Application: Be the catalyst for growth in someone else's life today through honest, constructive feedback.\nSystem: \nSystem: WEATHER\nSystem: Los Angeles: ☀️ 57°F. Clear skies, cool morning.\nSystem: \nSystem: TODAY'S PRIORITY\nSystem: Resolve the Lego freight sortation reject issue. Eliminate the excess label bottleneck.\nSystem: \nSystem: FAMILY FOCUS\nSystem: Put the phone away and have 15 minutes of undivided, active engagement with Daylynn and Lil Deuce.\nSystem: \nSystem: COACHING FOCUS\nSystem: Execution over Intent. Shift the focus from \"trying\" to \"completing\" the standard.\nSystem: \nSystem: STOIC PRINCIPLE\nSystem: Dichotomy of Control. Focus exclusively on your effort and your reaction; ignore the noise of external chaos.\nSystem: \nSystem: PERSONAL DISCIPLINE\nSystem: Zero procrastination. Attack the hardest task on the list first.\nSystem: \nSystem: TONIGHT'S QUESTION\nSystem: Where did I compromise my standard today, and how will I correct it tomorrow?\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/dai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 22nd, 2026 - 6:56 AM (America/Los_Angeles) / 2026-04-22 13:56 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776866194450}}
