{"type":"message","id":"9883214e","parentId":"04b7ac74","timestamp":"2026-04-30T08:28:39.013Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-20 17:23:54 PDT] GOOD MORNING, D! ☀️\nSystem: \nSystem: **TODAY'S FOCUS**\nSystem: Precision and Presence. Lead with intention in every room you enter today.\nSystem: \nSystem: **FAMILY**\nSystem: Be the anchor. Prioritize a moment of undivided attention for the kids and a meaningful connection with your wife. Small wins in the home lead to big wins in life.\nSystem: \nSystem: **COACHING**\nSystem: Standard-setting. Don't just teach the skill; coach the effort. Hold the line on discipline while fueling their confidence.\nSystem: \nSystem: **PERSONAL DISCIPLINE**\nSystem: Win the morning to own the day. Stick to your routine, keep your workspace clean, and execute your tasks with zero friction.\nSystem: \nSystem: **TONIGHT CHECK-IN**\nSystem: - Did I lead by example today?\nSystem: - Where did I provide the most value?\nSystem: - Is tomorrow's plan locked in?\nSystem: \nSystem: Stay sharp. Let's get it. 🚀\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/dai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 20th, 2026 - 5:26 PM (America/Los_Angeles) / 2026-04-21 00:26 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776731195921}}
