{"type":"message","id":"1aaa06bc","parentId":"b83b9ff9","timestamp":"2026-04-30T08:28:39.017Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-24 06:32:23 PDT] GOOD MORNING\nSystem: \nSystem: **BIBLE:** Philippians 4:13 - \"I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me.\" *Application: When the day feels too heavy or complex, anchor yourself to this source of strength. Don't rely solely on your own willpower; delegate the difficulty upward.*\nSystem: \nSystem: **WEATHER:** Clear skies expected. No significant weather disruptions are forecast, but monitor the afternoon traffic flow—expect congestion near the I-10 interchange.\nSystem: \nSystem: **TODAY'S PRIORITY:** Complete the review and sign-off documentation for the Lego freight sortation issue in WebEC. Make this a closed loop by 3 PM.\nSystem: \nSystem: **FAMILY FOCUS:** Dedicate 20 minutes to playing a game *without* looking at phones, tablets, or screens with Daylynn and Lil Deuce. Full presence only.\nSystem: \nSystem: **COACHING FOCUS:** Leadership by *anticipation*. Don't wait for problems to present themselves; actively observe the system (work/home/team) and address the weak points before they become failures.\nSystem: \nSystem: **STOIC PRINCIPLE:** Control what's controllable. The Lego rejects are external friction. Your control point is the quality and thoroughness of *your* investigative work. Keep your focus there.\nSystem: \nSystem: **PERSONAL DISCIPLINE:** No reactive scrolling. If you feel the urge to check non-essential feeds, immediately redirect the energy to organizing one physical space (desk corner, tool rack, etc.) for 5 minutes.\nSystem: \nSystem: **TONIGHT'S QUESTION:** Where today did I choose the path of least resistance, and what was the actual cost of that convenience?\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/dai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Friday, April 24th, 2026 - 6:56 AM (America/Los_Angeles) / 2026-04-24 13:56 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777038994079}}
