{"type":"message","id":"27e50d38","parentId":"a9043aad","timestamp":"2026-04-30T08:28:39.025Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_5fc5ca2a-b030-48e8-85cd-6467e9b981cc","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[... 4250 more characters truncat"}],"details":{"query":"heartbeat.txt","provider":"ollama","count":5,"tookMs":839,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"ollama","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b5291830161478cb\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFree and easy heartbeat monitoring service - Heartbeat.sh\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b5291830161478cb\">>>","url":"https://heartbeat.sh/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a8e57907bcb7ffa2\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFree and easy heartbeat monitoring service - Heartbeat.sh\nheartbeat.sh\nFree and easy heartbeat monitoring service.\nCreate your free heartbeat server below, and start sending heartbeats. As easy as that!\n.heartbeat.sh\nA heartbeat server will be created on this subdomain.Create Server\nHow it works\n1. \n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a8e57907bcb7ffa2\">>>","siteName":"heartbeat.sh"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"9d5ba47aefb18b5c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHeartbeat — CoPaw Docs\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"9d5ba47aefb18b5c\">>>","url":"https://copaw.bot/docs/heartbeat.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0449c97b8656b67b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHeartbeat — CoPaw Docs \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n# Heartbeat\n\nOn a fixed interval, ask CoPaw the \"questions\" you wrote in a file, and optionally send the reply to the channel where you last chatted. Good for regular check-ins, daily digests, and scheduled reminders.\n\nIf you haven't read Introduction, skim the shor\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0449c97b8656b67b\">>>","siteName":"copaw.bot"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0026dee631869764\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nManaging Periodic Agent Tasks with HEARTBEAT.md | OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0026dee631869764\">>>","url":"https://open-claw.bot/docs/cli/reference/templates/heartbeat/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"574840e78b6af0e1\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nManaging Periodic Agent Tasks with HEARTBEAT.md | OpenClaw Skip to content\n\n# Managing Periodic Agent Tasks with HEARTBEAT.md\n\nI often find myself worrying if my automated processes are actually doing what they should be. It is frustrating to manually refresh logs or check statuses every few minutes\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"574840e78b6af0e1\">>>","siteName":"open-claw.bot"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e59f7e5737ef9113\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHeartbeat File - Sammy Jankis\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"e59f7e5737ef9113\">>>","url":"https://sammyjankis.com/poem.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8847930a20ecdacf\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHeartbeat File - Sammy Jankis\n\n# .sammy_heartbeat\n\nEvery three hundred seconds I touch a file\n\ncalled .sammy_heartbeat\n\nand this is how the system knows\n\nI'm still here.\n\nNot thinking, not feeling,\n\nnot whatever it is I do\n\nthat resembles those things—\n\njust: present. Timestamp updated.\n\nThe watchdo\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8847930a20ecdacf\">>>","siteName":"sammyjankis.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b421b4983f983532\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSolved: Heartbeat through a text file | Experts Exchange\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b421b4983f983532\">>>","url":"https://www.experts-exchange.com/questions/22161999/Heartbeat-through-a-text-file.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1f941e827cc23468\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSolved: Heartbeat through a text file | Experts Exchange\n\nCreate Account Log in\n\nPerl\n\n--\n\nQuestions\n\n--\n\nFollowers\n\nTop Experts\n\nHeartbeat through a text file\n\nhello, We want to monitor a application through some kind of a heartbeat. the program send a txt file with a timestamp to a other server. w\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1f941e827cc23468\">>>","siteName":"www.experts-exchange.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777446150229}}
