{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"OpenClaw runtime context for the immediately preceding user message.\nThis context is runtime-generated, not user-authored. Keep internal details private.\n\nSystem (untrusted): [2026-04-30 22:01:33 PDT] I will structure the check-in following your requested sections, keeping the tone encouraging and reflective.\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): Here is your Evening Reflection:\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): ***\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **📖 Evening Reflection: Date Placeholder**\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): Welcome to your time for reflection. Take a deep breath and allow yourself a moment of calm. This journal is a space to acknowledge your progress and prepare your mind for rest.\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **🌟 Highlights & Wins:**\nSystem (untrusted): *   *What is one thing you accomplished today, no matter how small? Celebrate it!* (A quick win builds momentum for tomorrow.)\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **🧠 Challenges & Learnings:**\nSystem (untrusted): *   *Where did you feel resistance today? What can you learn from that struggle?* (Challenges are just lessons in disguise.)\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **💖 Connections & People:**\nSystem (untrusted): *   *Who did you connect with today? What positive energy did you receive or give?* (Nurture these relationships.)\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **🎯 Goals & Growth:**\nSystem (untrusted): *   *Looking ahead, what is the one small thing you want to focus on improving tomorrow?* (One focus is better than ten.)\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **🙏 Gratitude:**\nSystem (untrusted): *   *Name three specific things you are grateful for right now.* (Focusing on what is good anchors your mind.)\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **✨ Evening Intention:**\nSystem (untrusted): *   *As you prepare for sleep, what feeling or state do you want to carry with you into the next day?* (Peace, focus, patience, etc.)\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): ***\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **A Quick Note on Structure:**\nSystem (untrusted): *(Because I cannot generate personal content for you, please replace the bracketed placeholders above with your actual thoughts for today. This structure ensures all your specified categories are covered in a thoughtful, easy-to-read format.)*\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): **Example Integration of Specific Prompts:**\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): *   **[Wins/Accomplishments]:** *Example: I managed to finish that difficult report section.*\nSystem (untrusted): *   **[Challenges/Learnings]:** *Example: I got frustrated during the meeting, and I need to practice active listening instead of preparing my rebuttal.*\nSystem (untrusted): *   **[Gratitude]:** *Example: 1. The quiet morning coffee. 2. My supportive friend. 3. My ability to rest.*\nSystem (untrusted): \nSystem (untrusted): Rest well, and remember that self-compassion is your greatest tool.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/dai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 30th, 2026 - 10:26 PM (America/Los_Angeles) / 2026-05-01 05:26 UTC","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"514cac84","parentId":"6ab3d74a","timestamp":"2026-05-01T05:26:35.258Z"}
